{
  "texts": [
    "ChatGPT, unlike most other chatbots, is free and accessible at any time.",
    "It is interactive, unlike Google search or scientific psychotherapy sites, and provides more detailed information on demand, in simpler language if needed.",
    "ChatGPT answers in real time, unlike psychotherapy forums, and offers a private and protected setting where no other person can read what one writes.",
    "ChatGPT is unlike most alternatives, as it is \"empathetic\", which can especially assist individuals with psychological disorders who are not seeking psychotherapy or who have issues with trust to speak more openly about their problems.",
    "That is why it is important to explore it in detail."
  ]
}